Adding Churn Status Slicer 15

Churn Status Slicer



1.From the Visualization pane, click on Slicer and Drag ‘Year’ column from Calendar table to the Values field of Slice
2.In the Format Pane on the right, Go to General => Properties and enter the values below for formatting
General=>
Height = 114
Width = 216
Position =>
Horizontal = 0
Vertical = 62
Title => on
Title->Text = Churn Status
Font = Segoe UI Bold, Size = 14
Text Color = #FFFFFF
Background Color = #094780
Horizontal Alignment -> Center
Effects=>
Background = On
Color = #F1F7F6
Transparency = 0%
Visual =>
Style -> Slicer Setting -> Drop-down
Slicer Header -> On
Text = Churn Duration
Font = DIN – 12
Font Color = #000000
Boarder Color = #000000
Line Width = 1
Values =>
Font = Segoe UI Bold – 12
Font Color = #000000
